quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,By the morning brightness
  93,2,and the night when it is still
  93,3,your Lord has not abandoned you nor does He hate you
  93,4,The Last will be better for you than the First
  93,5,Your Lord will soon give to you and you will be satisfied
  93,6,Did He not find you orphaned and shelter you
  93,7,Did He not find you wandering and guide you
  93,8,Did He not find you impoverished and enrich you
  93,9,"So as for orphans, do not oppress them"
  93,10,"and as for beggars, do not berate them"
  93,11,"And as for the blessing of your Lord, speak out"